          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "9Be reaction target with thickness of 188 mg/cm2"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 58Ni primary beam was accelerated through",
                "the K500/K1200 cyclotrons to an energy 160MeV/A",
                "and fragmented on a 802 mg/cm2 9Be production target.",
                "Fragments were separated by the A1900 separator",
                "into a cocktail beam that contained 49Fe in one",
                "setting of the A1900 and 49V in another. The fragment",
                "beam rates for 49Fe was 300 pps and for 49V beam rate",
                "was 2E+5 particles per second. The secondary beams",
                "were identified by measuring their time of flight",
                "between two plastic scintillator detectors, one",
                "located after the A1900 fragment separator and the",
                "other in the S800 analysis beam line."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOFDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Identification of reaction products"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP",
                "IOCH",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Reaction products were identified",
                "in the S800 by measuring the energy loss in an",
                "ionization chamber in conjunction with ToF measured",
                "between  scintillators in the beam line"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma rays were measured using the",
                "gamma-ray array GRETINA, consisting of nine detector",
                "modules, each comprising four high-purity germanium",
                "crystals. Four of these modules were centred at 58 deg",
                "and five centred at 90 deg in relation to the beam",
                "direction. To maximise photopeak efficiency and",
                "optimise the coincidence analysis, an add-back",
                "procedure was applied in which energies deposited",
                "in neighbouring GRETINA crystals were summed"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
